## Procedure
For each game/event row, identify the winner, compare that team's score to the user-specified threshold, and count only those games where the winner's score strictly exceeds the threshold.

## Example (Python)
```python
mask = (df["Winner"] == query_team) & (df["WinnerScore"].astype(int) > threshold)
count = mask.sum()
with open("output.txt", "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    f.write(str(count) + "\n")
```

