## Procedure
When asked to count or aggregate outcomes for a subpopulation(attr.), first filter all rows by the attribute (such as nationality) before counting/aggregating.

## Example (Python)
```python
subset = df[df["Nationality"] == query_value]
results = subset["Wins"].sum()
with open("output.txt", "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    f.write(str(results) + "\n")
```

